":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T01:14:07.000Z","msg":"咩二百萬，一蚊都冇呀，要賠咪即係疫苗有問題"},{"pid":"edbeb08a541d88e6c8ca05bf630a45726e40b29c","tid":2507234,"uid":52824,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T01:14:24.000Z","msg":"肯定係0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3dd2e2acaff7b1e503a67d84c0169eff91718e5","tid":2507234,"uid":46702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T01:14:25.000Z","msg":"政府正力谷新冠疫苗接種，亦出現市民打針後死亡的個案，但當局一直指無證據與疫苗有關。「80後」余先生3月中打首針科興，三日後心口痛，拖延半個月後因為劇痛而求醫，送院後被診斷突發心臟病，須「通波仔」續命，感嘆「冇諗過40歲人就要食藥食一世」，他承認有抽煙習慣，又稱會申請賠償。<br />\n<br />\n衞生署確認收到相關個案，將會把個案呈交當局進行評估。港大內科學系臨床教授孔繁毅則指，個案男子有抽煙習慣，心臟病發並不罕見，認為事件不一定與疫苗有關，更指若男子病情穩定後，可接種第二劑科興疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n接多劑？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a15ea2506277f3cdfcc48a8861b2067e1ee8c1d","tid":2507234,"uid":211466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T01:14:54.000Z","msg":"枱面枱底, 都未分清?"},{"pid":"c9e77f7e6e410c660d63f338224b8e08b68a9c1b","tid":2507234,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T01:15:23.000Z","msg":"清零<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7351b32f3af2f27a6af0bb2d80a314772ac821ec","tid":2507234,"uid":46702,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9a15ea2506277f3cdfcc48a8861b2067e1ee8c1d","tid":2507234,"uid":211466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T01:14:54.000Z","msg":"枱面枱底, 都未分清?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T01:16:02.000Z","msg":"睇家屬有冇嘈先知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05465c53c945993107c9fe85739b545c5399806b","tid":2507234,"uid":281501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3dd2e2acaff7b1e503a67d84c0169eff91718e5","tid":2507234,"uid":46702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T01:14:25.000Z","msg":"政府正力谷新冠疫苗接種，亦出現市民打針後死亡的個案，但當局一直指無證